snippet: Paula Creamer and Jiyai Shin played until dark and still could not break their deadlock in the Kingsmill Championship in Williamsburg, Va.
abstract: Paula Creamer and Jiyai Shin are unable to break their deadlock in the Kingsmill Championship golf tournament, and will continue playoff.
